### Variables ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Paste the values from `bin/rails db:seed` output here.

@host = http://localhost:3000
@api_key = mk_dev_PASTE_FROM_SEED_OUTPUT
@hmac_secret = PASTE_FROM_SEED_OUTPUT
@sdk_public_key = sdk_dev_PASTE_FROM_SEED_OUTPUT
@shopper_id = shp_demo

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### EVENT INGESTION
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### X-Signature must be HMAC-SHA256("{Idempotency-Key}:{raw_body}", hmac_secret).
### The signed payload extends the brief (closes the in-window replay hole —
### see README "Design decisions / HMAC payload"). The seed prints a curl
### with a pre-computed signature for the smoke test.

### Ingest event (signature placeholder — recompute or use seed output)
POST {{host}}/v1/events
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}
Idempotency-Key: 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
X-Signature: PASTE_HMAC_SHA256_HEX
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shopper_id": "{{shopper_id}}",
  "event_type": "cart.updated",
  "occurred_at": "2026-05-27T02:00:00Z",
  "data": { "cart_total_cents": 7500, "currency": "USD", "item_count": 3 }
}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### CAMPAIGNS (merchant-facing CRUD)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List campaigns
GET {{host}}/v1/campaigns
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}

### Show campaign
GET {{host}}/v1/campaigns/1
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}

### Create campaign
POST {{host}}/v1/campaigns
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Free shipping over $50",
  "active": true,
  "trigger": {
    "event_type": "cart.updated",
    "conditions": [
      { "field": "data.cart_total_cents", "op": "gte", "value": 5000 }
    ]
  },
  "render": {
    "component": "banner",
    "payload": {
      "title": "You've unlocked free shipping",
      "body": "No code needed — applied at checkout",
      "cta": { "label": "Continue", "url": "/checkout" }
    }
  }
}

### Update campaign (pause it)
PATCH {{host}}/v1/campaigns/1
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "active": false }

### Delete campaign
DELETE {{host}}/v1/campaigns/1
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### SDK (browser-facing)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get theme (browser side, public key auth)
GET {{host}}/v1/sdk/theme
Authorization: Bearer {{sdk_public_key}}

### Mint SDK session token (server-to-server, merchant secret auth)
POST {{host}}/v1/sdk/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "shopper_id": "{{shopper_id}}" }

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Health
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Liveness (used by Docker healthcheck)
GET {{host}}/up
